LEX The Critic.

"First Person" is a person.
"Critic" is a person.
"Keystone" is a person.
"Round Classification" is a text.
"Next Lead" is a text.

The First Person appoints the Critic, and appoints the Keystone.

CLAUSE: Classify.
The Critic may register the Round Classification, and afterwards send the Next Lead to the Keystone.
